Thomas
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[618,749,1867,1889]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3" rank="species">new species</taxonomicNameLabel>
. Male genitalia. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[926,949,1867,1889]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3">6)</emphasis>
Aedeagus. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1072,1095,1867,1889]" pageId="4" pageNumber="3">7)</emphasis>
